markets.title: Will any New Heights video get more than 25 Million views a week after upload?
markets.rules_primary: If New Heights uploads a video that receives more than 25 million million views the day after the upload date at 10:00 AM ET, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The target video must be uploading Starting Aug 12, 2025 and before Aug 14, 2025. A new episode New Heights with Taylor Swift is expected to be released Wednesday, August 12, 2025; if so, this market will resolve based on the number of views at 10:00 AM ET on Thursday, August 13, 2025.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
